{"tid":2220945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（港台工會抗議打壓利君雅）入嚟一人一信撐利君雅","createTime":"2020-09-28T04:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:10:13.000Z","uid":325840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07822df8952ab6de81bd9f01bbcf766afa1cfb92","tid":2220945,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3502311406521121/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3502311406521121%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUtXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=f6d0e3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3502311406521121/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港電台延長記者利君雅試用期 120 日，並「重開」對她去年 7 月起，記者會上表現的調查；港台工會今早趁港台顧問委員會開會時，在會議室外抗議，批評事件是政治打壓，認為港台是因商經局施壓，要求新任顧委會主席林大輝遵守約章，勿干預編採運作。今日亦是剛出任港台顧委會主席的林大輝上任後第一次會議，早上林大輝與廣播處長梁家榮等人進入會議室時，回應記者提問。。。。<br />\n<br />\n趙善恩稱，之前利君雅已就投訴接受過一次調查，但調查已結案，不理解為何又重啟調查，「法庭都唔會一案兩審」，相信港台是被商經局施壓。<br />\n<br />\n趙善恩又反問，<span class=\"red\">是否接獲多宗投訴</span>，便代表同事工作有問題，認為網上難免會有「haters(憎恨者）」，港台的做法會影響員工履行職責，尖銳提問本就是記者的責任，卻因「haters」而被調查。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲投訴就調查，黃絲感謝信當睇唔到？<br />\n<br />\n利君雅比大量人投訴去信港台長，1人1信去港台支持利君雅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426431</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<span class=\"medium\"><strong><strong></strong></strong></span><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n致香港電台：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港電台的長期觀眾。我想對利君雅記者作出簡單而直接的感謝。<br />\n<br />\n利君雅記者在香港動盪的時候，發揮出色的記者工作。對官員的問題一針見血，對政府種種迴避的態度加以追問。對社會現狀有獨到見解，以理性及中立的態度去揭示香港種種問題。<br />\n<br />\n請香港電台，代本人向利君雅記者轉達謝意。亦希望香港電台可以繼續保持中立，以事實報道真相。<br />\n<br />\nDear RTHK,<br />\n<br />\nI am a RTHK regular audience for many years. I would like to express my sincerest gratitude to journalist Ms. Nabela Qoser. She has shown bravery and the spirit of being a journalist, seeking the truth during this difficult time in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nI am no expert in journalism but Ms. Nabela Qoser have raised questions in the recent press conferences that many of us have wanted to ask. She has revealed the truth that I needed to see with facts and evidence.<br />\n<br />\nPlease pass on my greatest appreciation to Ms. Nabela Qoser&rsquo;s outstanding work and dedication. We need more reporters like her.<br />\n<br />\nxxx<br />\n<br />\n28/9/2020"},{"pid":"03a2ca21e298c8f06bfb975e2f54c5a495c5f62b","tid":2220945,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2134fe6f56aeb158ee5296ae00b1ed86ed5f96","tid":2220945,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b16896e2254f92d044ae2906fe01d237b05edb","tid":2220945,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6939fe3b3b6e57a10bb2af641b7b74241a94d49","tid":2220945,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dabe8051adee597c84cf9c94de43aab6b46fa4","tid":2220945,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid